Synopsis:
After the goblin hunt celebration party, the Drow Commander Minthara has made arrangements to get intimate with the player at night.

After the sex scene, Minthara becomes troubled. She realises that while she's with the player she cannot hear the voice of the Absolute... which is liberating, and disturbing. This, unknown to her, is because of the Astral Prism's influence.
